com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.snomedrefset

Interface SnomedSimpleMapRefSetMember

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SnomedRefSetMember
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    SnomedComplexMapRefSetMember
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rf2RefSetMember, SnomedComplexMapRefSetMemberImpl, SnomedSimpleMapRefSetMemberImpl, UnsupportedRf2RefSetMember

    public interface SnomedSimpleMapRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    Representation of a SNOMED CT simple map type reference set member. The purpose of this kind of reference set member is to support mapping between SNOMED CT ontology and any other terminologies by pointing terminology components from different terminologies.

    The following features are supported:

    • Map Target Component Id
    • Map Target Component Type

    See Also:
    SnomedRefSetPackage.getSnomedSimpleMapRefSetMember()
